metadata.name: Architect was born. Created to create.
metadata.description:
Deadlines & Ambitions.

Not be afraid, pursue our desires,
Time is running out to make the followers continue to believe in our offerings.

Realistic & Artificiality Layer.

We always have two sides. The first side, they don't need to know it deeply. It's enough to know our second side & make them continue to trust & bond with their interest in what we do. They know that the result. They want it what the fake we made. We pamper them so they drown in it.

Dramas and Technology.

Projecting the new things with lure of the future is a must.
Either they want to call it 1.0 / 2.0 / 3.0 or so on, we will present it, because time will always run for making movies, they played roles on the stage we created.



[Black Scenario]
